Generate parquet output file

write_forecast.Rd

Generate parquet output file

Usage

write_forecast(
  da_forecast_output,
  use_s3 = FALSE,
  bucket = NULL,
  endpoint = NULL,
  local_directory = NULL
)

Arguments

da_forecast_output

list; object that is returned by run_da_forecast()

use_s3

Boolen; use s3 storage for saving scores

bucket

S3 bucket

endpoint

S3 endpoint

local_directory

local directory of scores if not using s3

Value

None

Details

Function generates a parquet file from the object that is returned by run_da_forecast()

Quinn Thomas
